OL,3,CHarry Styles congratulates London
OL,4,Cschool shortlisted in global education
OL,5,Cprize
OL,7,FHarry Styles has congratulated a
OL,8,FLondon school after it was shortlisted
OL,9,Ffor a global education prize.
OL,11,FSwiss Cottage School, Development and
OL,12,FResearch Centre, a state primary and
OL,13,Fsecondary special school in north-west
OL,14,FLondon, is among five UK schools in
OL,15,Fthe top 10 list for the World's Best
OL,16,FSchool Prizes this year.
OL,18,FThe others shortlisted are:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
