OL,3,CHarry Styles congratulates London
OL,4,Cschool shortlisted in global education
OL,5,Cprize
OL,7,FThe former One Direction singer, whose
OL,8,Ffriend is a teacher at Swiss Cottage,
OL,9,Fsaid: "This is an amazing achievement
OL,10,Ffor the children, their families, the
OL,11,Fstaff, therapists, local partners and
OL,12,Fnational collaborators that help to
OL,13,Fmake this wonderful school so special.
OL,15,F"Keep doing what you're doing and
OL,16,Fcongratulations again."
OL,18,FChildren's author Julia Donaldson sent
OL,19,Fher good wishes to the pupils at Ward
OL,20,FJackson.
OL,26,@qD@GOUwD@AOUxD@WO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
