OL,3,CHarry Styles congratulates London
OL,4,Cschool shortlisted in global education
OL,5,Cprize
OL,7,FShe said in a video message:
OL,8,F"Congratulations, that's a huge
OL,9,Fachievement for quite a small school
OL,10,Fand I was also very pleased to hear
OL,11,Fyou like my stories, not just that you
OL,12,Flike reading them but I hear you've
OL,13,Fbeen acting them and drawing them and
OL,14,Fgetting to really know the characters
OL,15,Fso that's great as well."
OL,17,FVikas Pota, founder of T4 Education
OL,18,Fand the prize, said the five settings
OL,19,Fhave shown that "British schools truly
OL,20,Fstand among the best in the world".
